Description: Beremiz is an Open Source framework for automation
 With Beremiz, you can :
    - Automate everything.
    - Take any processor into a PLC.
    - Program once, run anywhere.
    - Create PLC controled customizable HMIs.
    - Conform to standards.
    - Avoid vendor lock.
